    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Depending on the case, one could use sub queries, something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>select e\nfrom Entity e\nwhere e.id in\n(\n  select e.id\n  from Entity2 e2\n       join e2.entity e\n  where e2.someProperty = 'value'\n)\n      or e.id in\n(\n  select e.id\n  from Entity3 e3\n       join e3.entity e\n  where e3.someProperty = 'value2'\n)\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
