      "comment_id" : 84135703,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Errm nope. JPQL has no &quot;UNION&quot; as all answers tell you. The only way that a JPA provider will accept that is if it provides a VENDOR EXTENSION. And has the OP said what JPA provider is used? Nope."
    } ],
